snippet.title: Ribbit for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

A Frogger clone. Try to make it from one side to the other, while avoiding cars and hop on the turtles and logs in the right moment.

Also watch the timer!


What I think:

Nice game, but you have to get used to the controls first.
